            <br>

            <%= link_to '#sign-up-form-container', :class => "btn btn-red btn-large", :style => "margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:0px;width:500px;font-size:24px;" do %>
              <i class="icon-arrow-right"></i> Sign Up Now
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
        </div> 

        <div class="row-fluid" style="margin-top:20px;">
          <div class="span12">
            <div class="padded" style="background-color: #f5f5f5;border: 2px solid #d2d2d2;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;">
              <div>
                <strong class="blue" style="font-size:24px;">"</strong><em>  I have been using Zenmaid since they launched this amazing software! I can use it anywhere with my tablet, smart phone or computer. I love that it sends my clients a reminder for the scheduled service every time. This has saved me an enormous amount of time! If you have a small cleaning business or an established business look no further, this software will save you time and money!</em><strong class="blue" style="font-size:24px;">"</strong><br>
              </div>
